      <title>德意志银行聘请 Perella 的 Andy Tam 担任保险联席主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/deutsche-bank-hires-perella-s-andy-tam-as-co-head-of-insurance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德意志银行聘请 Perella Weinberg Partners 董事总经理 Andy Tam 与 Scott Littlejohn 一起担任美洲保险联席主管。]]></description>
